AUDIO: 'The advancements in AI music generation are getting more and more exciting every day and I\'ve got some really cool stuff to show you today. Welcome back to the channel where we discuss the creative uses of AI and Ace Studio is a piece of software I have covered a few times on this channel and it just gets'

